snippet.title: Arcade Game: Heart Attack (1983 Century Electronics)
snippet.description:
A horrible maze game where you fill the maze with dots. Drop a plug to block the enemy or freeze the enemy for five seconds. You must complete the maze before time runs out.

Note: Used cheats in this game and to skip some repeated levels. The game is endless.
